WEBVTT

00:24.040 --> 00:24.880
Marquis.

00:25.920 --> 00:28.840
Two female military physicians
from the supply unit

00:28.920 --> 00:29.960
request an audience.

00:33.840 --> 00:34.760
Female physicians?

00:38.840 --> 00:39.680
Let them in.

00:41.320 --> 00:42.880
Marquis, you'd better prepare yourself.

01:00.800 --> 01:02.600
I've temporarily taken on
the role of Imperial Physician

01:02.680 --> 01:04.560
and come on His Majesty's behalf
for the army's morale.

01:05.600 --> 01:08.440
Along the way, I heard you were trapped
in the Wu River mountains,

01:08.520 --> 01:09.640
so I changed course to come here.

01:09.720 --> 01:11.920
You slipped out
during incense prayers, didn't you?

01:13.960 --> 01:16.760
This is a battlefield,
not a place for you to have fun.

01:16.840 --> 01:19.320
If you try to play clever again,
the consequences will be disastrous.

01:19.920 --> 01:21.360
Anyway,

01:21.440 --> 01:23.320
I'm blessed with good fortune,

01:24.480 --> 01:26.080
and with the Pig-Slaughter Squad
protecting me,

01:26.720 --> 01:29.160
I broke through the encirclement
and turned danger into safety.

01:29.840 --> 01:31.360
Someone's on the cliff. Loose arrows!

01:32.240 --> 01:33.760
Oh no, we've been spotted.

01:34.520 --> 01:35.240
Get down!

01:42.440 --> 01:43.360
Give me your hand.

01:55.960 --> 01:57.360
That was just luck.

01:57.440 --> 01:59.880
You happened to flee
right into the range of our archers.

02:01.040 --> 02:02.920
If Shi Yue's men had caught you,

02:03.000 --> 02:04.200
do you know what would have happened?

02:04.880 --> 02:07.560
At best, humiliation.
At worst, you'd be left in pieces.

02:15.120 --> 02:17.120
I acted rashly.

02:17.200 --> 02:18.560
I didn't think about any of that.

02:19.840 --> 02:22.440
Do whatever you want with me.

02:28.800 --> 02:31.240
Sir, the Strategist is calling for you.
There's official business to discuss.

02:33.480 --> 02:34.560
Strategist?

02:35.480 --> 02:39.680
Is that Headmaster Gongsun?

02:46.280 --> 02:49.120
Your Highness risked your life

02:49.640 --> 02:51.040
to come here

02:51.600 --> 02:54.080
for other intentions after all.

02:55.200 --> 02:57.200
You fight for the people, Marquis.

02:57.280 --> 02:59.040
As the Grand Princess,

02:59.120 --> 03:01.760
it is only right
that I concern myself with your safety.

03:01.840 --> 03:03.560
In that case,

03:03.640 --> 03:04.560
I'll arrange

03:05.160 --> 03:07.680
a separate tent for the army medics,

03:07.760 --> 03:10.400
in gratitude for His Majesty's
kind concern.

03:14.640 --> 03:17.480
-Xie Qi, escort the them to the quarters.
-Yes, sir.

03:18.760 --> 03:20.640
Thank you for your hospitality, Marquis.

03:23.760 --> 03:24.600
Please.

03:28.560 --> 03:30.000
Assign a few well-mannered soldiers

03:30.080 --> 03:31.200
to attend to the Grand Princess.

03:31.280 --> 03:33.440
Keep those lazy ruffians away.

03:34.200 --> 03:36.280
Don't let them cause trouble
or breach protocol.

03:37.040 --> 03:38.040
Understood, sir.

03:43.200 --> 03:44.680
The Pig-Slaughter Squad again.

05:12.080 --> 05:16.640
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:23.120 --> 05:24.120
It smells good.

05:25.640 --> 05:28.520
We've been running low on supplies.
Finally, something to eat today.

05:28.600 --> 05:30.800
I heard someone
delivered grain last night.

05:31.520 --> 05:34.160
Yeah, finally we can have a proper meal.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.720
Hey, do you know Yan Zheng?

05:36.800 --> 05:37.840
No, I don't.

05:40.840 --> 05:43.520
-Hey, do you know Yan Zheng?
-No, I don't.

05:44.200 --> 05:46.000
-Hey, do you know Yan Zheng?
-No, no, I don't.

05:46.080 --> 05:48.280
Hey, do you know Yan Zheng?

05:48.360 --> 05:49.400
No, I don't.

05:50.280 --> 05:52.520
-Do you know Yan Zheng?
-No idea.

05:53.280 --> 05:55.440
Hey, you two. Do you know Yan Zheng?

05:55.520 --> 05:56.440
A soldier from Lin'an.

05:56.520 --> 05:58.560
Never heard of him. Your husband?

06:01.880 --> 06:03.040
He's about this tall.

06:04.760 --> 06:07.280
Kind of long, big eyes.

06:07.840 --> 06:09.160
Has a mole right here on his nose.

06:10.400 --> 06:12.000
Looks a bit fierce when he's not smiling,

06:12.600 --> 06:15.600
but when he does, he seems
kind of simple. He's from Lin'an.

06:16.200 --> 06:17.280
Haven't seen him.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.760
Our unit has hundreds of men,

06:19.840 --> 06:21.520
in and out, day and night.

06:21.600 --> 06:22.880
Plenty we don't know.

06:22.960 --> 06:23.920
Yeah.

06:25.000 --> 06:27.000
-Thanks.
-No problem.

06:30.920 --> 06:32.440
This place sits three different troops.

06:32.520 --> 06:34.880
Over a thousand men.
Where are you going to find him?

06:36.160 --> 06:38.360
I saw that falcon delivering
a message down the mountain.

06:38.440 --> 06:39.760
I thought he might be up here.

06:40.920 --> 06:42.640
That husband of yours
is just a common soldier.

06:42.720 --> 06:44.640
Even if someone did know him,
who would remember?

06:53.920 --> 06:56.440
XIE

07:07.360 --> 07:08.720
Still thinking about
that husband of yours?

07:13.560 --> 07:14.480
I'm thinking…

07:16.960 --> 07:18.520
Maybe he's already been killed in battle.

07:25.160 --> 07:26.800
Can't a person
get some sleep at this hour?

07:28.160 --> 07:29.920
Which mountain did you come down from?

07:30.000 --> 07:32.680
-Go back to sleep.
-Alright, alright. No need to snap.

07:33.960 --> 07:34.840
Good thing you held me back,

07:34.920 --> 07:36.160
or I would've gone out there
and taken a swing at him.

07:42.840 --> 07:44.520
I've been thinking about something.

07:45.640 --> 07:48.000
Remember when a few of us
went to your place to collect a debt?

07:48.720 --> 07:50.240
How did that bunch of old folks,

07:50.320 --> 07:52.960
led by Mr. Zhao,
manage to beat us black and blue?

07:53.560 --> 07:54.920
Later, I figured it out.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.080
It had to be your husband's doing.

07:58.720 --> 08:01.200
So, you don't need to worry.

08:05.120 --> 08:06.360
You don't get it?

08:06.440 --> 08:07.320
He's saying

08:07.400 --> 08:09.920
your husband's kung fu
is just as good as yours.

08:11.400 --> 08:13.720
You guys deserved that beating last time.

08:16.040 --> 08:18.120
And why do you call him
"live-in husband" like that?

08:18.200 --> 08:19.280
Sounds weird.

08:21.120 --> 08:22.080
But I have to say,

08:22.160 --> 08:24.840
that live-in husband of yours
is really something.

08:24.920 --> 08:26.520
I'm Man Wu. Who do you think I am?

08:26.600 --> 08:28.440
When I locked eyes with him,

08:29.560 --> 08:30.960
I was shaking all over.

08:31.760 --> 08:32.919
Forget calling him "big brother."

08:33.000 --> 08:34.520
I'd call him "grandpa."

08:35.320 --> 08:36.480
Just call him "brother-in-law."

08:38.080 --> 08:39.799
From now on, we're family.

08:40.600 --> 08:42.000
Even Man Di here calls me "sister."

08:42.080 --> 08:43.240
Sister?

08:43.320 --> 08:44.280
Sister.

08:44.360 --> 08:45.200
Sister.

08:46.000 --> 08:46.880
Sister.

08:52.080 --> 08:52.920
What?

08:53.840 --> 08:54.960
You trying to take advantage of me?

08:55.680 --> 08:57.800
Let me tell you something. I will never
call you "sister" in this lifetime.

08:58.680 --> 08:59.720
You just did.

08:59.800 --> 09:01.560
Did I? Did I just call her "sister"?

09:01.640 --> 09:03.240
See? You just did it again. Didn't you?

09:04.120 --> 09:06.520
You little… You looking for a beating?

09:06.600 --> 09:08.480
You're going back on your word.

09:08.560 --> 09:10.240
-Don't move.
-Like I'm scared of you.

09:10.840 --> 09:13.560
-Come here.
-Sister, he hit me.

09:13.640 --> 09:15.200
-Sister.
-You little…

09:15.280 --> 09:16.600
-I'll hit you with this bench.
-No.

09:16.680 --> 09:18.040
I already told you once.

09:18.120 --> 09:19.280
Still at it?

09:19.360 --> 09:20.920
-What, you want me to tuck you in?
-I am going back to sleep.

09:21.000 --> 09:21.960
Can't sleep?

09:22.040 --> 09:23.040
Here, let me help you with that.

09:23.120 --> 09:23.960
‎Let me help you.

09:24.040 --> 09:25.640
Bring it on. I'll put you to sleep.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.400
Bro, I'm wrong.

09:27.480 --> 09:29.200
Bro.

09:29.880 --> 09:30.840
I'm awake now!

09:30.920 --> 09:31.840
Mercy!

09:31.920 --> 09:33.920
Could you go a little easier?

09:34.000 --> 09:35.520
-Off to sleep now?
-Mercy!

10:41.120 --> 10:42.920
Sir, you're injured.

10:43.000 --> 10:45.280
Leave the patrol to us.

10:47.480 --> 10:49.640
Alright. You go ahead.

12:41.120 --> 12:43.680
Step back. The Marquis has ordered

12:43.760 --> 12:46.280
that you, Physician,
are not to leave the tent.

12:47.440 --> 12:49.760
We must have a lot of wounded soldiers
at camp, don't we?

12:51.520 --> 12:54.080
There are quite a few,
but we've already arranged for their care.

12:54.160 --> 12:55.520
No need to trouble yourself, Physician.

12:56.360 --> 12:59.280
You're clearly short on medics.
Why won't you let me help?

13:00.280 --> 13:01.680
They're just rough soldiers.

13:01.760 --> 13:04.200
Don't know how to watch their mouths.
Afraid they might offend you.

13:04.880 --> 13:07.160
Which matters more,
protocol or people's lives?

13:07.960 --> 13:10.360
Do you want to watch your comrades suffer?

13:36.400 --> 13:37.400
I told you.

13:37.480 --> 13:38.680
This place isn't suitable for you.

13:38.760 --> 13:40.200
Go back to your tent and rest.

13:48.360 --> 13:51.120
This bone's been set wrong.
It needs to be broken and reset.

13:51.800 --> 13:52.640
What?

13:53.240 --> 13:56.360
I just got this wrapped. Why should I
listen to you and break it again?

13:56.440 --> 13:58.040
You haven't even touched it.

13:58.120 --> 13:59.920
-You got some kind of magic eyes?
-How dare you!

14:00.520 --> 14:01.840
You little…

14:01.920 --> 14:02.920
This is…

14:04.160 --> 14:06.560
an imperial physician from the palace.
Show some respect.

14:06.640 --> 14:07.920
Master Wu,

14:08.000 --> 14:09.160
I get it.

14:09.240 --> 14:11.000
Actually, my leg's almost healed.

14:11.080 --> 14:13.480
Look, look.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.680
I can walk on it. See?

14:15.760 --> 14:17.320
No need to break it and reset it.

14:17.400 --> 14:19.160
-Breaking it would hurt.
-Stop moving.

14:19.240 --> 14:20.160
I'm fine.

14:21.160 --> 14:22.520
-Sit down.
-Okay.

14:23.120 --> 14:24.640
-Rest up.
-Okay.

14:25.240 --> 14:26.520
Okay.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.720
Get some rest.

14:38.360 --> 14:39.640
This medicine only treats
the symptoms, not the root.

14:47.360 --> 14:50.560
For this wound, we need
to scrape off the dead tissue first,

14:50.640 --> 14:52.280
apply Wound Salve externally,

14:52.360 --> 14:53.960
and take a detoxifying decoction
internally.

14:54.040 --> 14:55.160
You'll recover quickly.

14:56.000 --> 14:57.480
What is Wound Salve?

14:57.560 --> 14:59.160
The key ingredient is lingzhi.

14:59.240 --> 15:00.600
The rest are just common herbs.

15:00.680 --> 15:02.040
Lingzhi?

15:02.120 --> 15:03.280
Imperial Physician,

15:03.360 --> 15:05.600
shouldn't you throw in

15:05.680 --> 15:06.680
some ginseng for us too?

15:11.320 --> 15:12.160
No need.

15:12.760 --> 15:14.360
Ginseng is too heating. It's not suitable.

15:19.680 --> 15:20.520
Imperial Physician,

15:21.480 --> 15:22.840
I don't know

15:22.920 --> 15:24.760
if your lingzhi can cure me,

15:24.840 --> 15:28.080
but it'd be enough
to buy me a few lives over.

15:28.160 --> 15:30.520
A mangy mutt like you
doesn't deserve lingzhi.

15:30.600 --> 15:32.000
Tree bark is more your speed.

15:32.600 --> 15:34.560
How dare you! Show some respect!

15:34.640 --> 15:35.520
Enough!

15:36.120 --> 15:37.040
All of you, stop laughing.

15:37.120 --> 15:38.400
Wounds don't hurt anymore?

15:38.480 --> 15:39.320
Dismissed.

15:40.800 --> 15:41.840
Of course it hurts.

15:41.920 --> 15:43.160
How could it not?

15:44.240 --> 15:45.600
A military camp like this

15:45.680 --> 15:47.720
doesn't even have these common medicines?

15:49.280 --> 15:51.200
You lived in the palace and wouldn't know.

15:51.280 --> 15:52.880
In our army,

15:52.960 --> 15:54.840
even having these common medicines
is a luxury.

15:55.440 --> 15:57.480
We don't dare hope
for those precious ones.

16:14.200 --> 16:15.360
You all were way too rude just now.

16:15.920 --> 16:17.320
She's still an imperial physician,
after all.

16:18.120 --> 16:22.040
Master Wu, if we die in battle,
at least our families get compensation.

16:22.120 --> 16:25.160
But if we get killed
by this female physician,

16:25.240 --> 16:26.480
that's just a raw deal.

16:27.080 --> 16:28.080
Exactly.

16:30.800 --> 16:33.520
MARQUIS WU'AN

16:36.360 --> 16:37.400
Straighten your arms.

17:02.120 --> 17:03.440
With skills like Yan Zheng's,

17:03.520 --> 17:05.200
he's usually pretty capable.

17:05.280 --> 17:06.520
He shouldn't have ended up
this badly injured.

17:07.200 --> 17:09.160
No, look at these wounded soldiers.

17:09.240 --> 17:10.359
Every one of them big and strong,

17:10.440 --> 17:13.760
built tougher than your husband.
And look at the state they're in.

17:13.839 --> 17:17.400
Once you're on the battlefield, you never
know when you might lose an arm or a leg.

17:18.720 --> 17:19.960
Forget I said that.

17:20.040 --> 17:22.319
May all the gods protect your husband.
Protect us all.

17:22.400 --> 17:24.000
Even if he loses an arm or a leg,
I'll take care of him.

17:25.160 --> 17:26.960
He escaped from Chongzhou before,

17:27.040 --> 17:28.400
covered in wounds,

17:28.480 --> 17:30.040
and I nursed him back then.

17:30.120 --> 17:31.720
How well did he recover?

17:36.480 --> 17:38.840
-Mrs. Fan.
-Mr. Sun.

17:40.640 --> 17:41.880
What are you doing here?

17:43.280 --> 17:44.800
The Pig-Slaughter Squad.

17:44.880 --> 17:46.800
What are you doing here?

17:48.840 --> 17:49.920
You're here for Changning, aren't you?

17:51.040 --> 17:52.400
Changning's here?

17:53.560 --> 17:54.440
She's here.

17:54.520 --> 17:56.200
She's not here. Come with me.

18:14.240 --> 18:16.080
Sister.

18:32.560 --> 18:33.760
Ning.

18:38.680 --> 18:40.520
Come here. Let me look at you.

18:43.520 --> 18:45.280
I finally found you.

18:46.520 --> 18:50.680
Sister, you finally came for me.

18:50.760 --> 18:53.040
I missed you so much.

18:55.280 --> 18:58.520
That bad man came to Lin'an
and killed people.

19:01.640 --> 19:03.400
Slow down. No need to rush.

19:03.480 --> 19:04.880
And Bao'er…

19:04.960 --> 19:10.360
Pretty Lady shouldn't go
with that bad man with white hair.

19:10.440 --> 19:12.680
Brother-in-law fought the bad man.

19:12.760 --> 19:14.520
He saved me.

19:14.600 --> 19:16.320
He got hurt.

19:17.120 --> 19:18.360
Brother-in-law's hurt?

19:20.560 --> 19:22.200
Where did you meet him?

19:22.280 --> 19:23.480
When?

19:27.560 --> 19:28.720
Bad weeds grow tall.

19:29.760 --> 19:30.720
You can rest easy, Mrs. Fan.

19:31.320 --> 19:33.320
He's tough. Not so easy to kill.

19:35.320 --> 19:37.400
Mr. Sun, you know where Yan Zheng is?

19:40.400 --> 19:41.280
He…

19:44.000 --> 19:45.080
Quick, come help.

19:45.160 --> 19:47.040
-Hurry up.
-Move it.

19:49.400 --> 19:50.240
Coming.

19:51.080 --> 19:53.080
What happened? Why so many wounded?

19:54.360 --> 19:56.640
Strategist, a small enemy force
tried to breach the mountain.

19:56.720 --> 19:57.760
They've fallen into our formation.
Half are dead.

19:58.360 --> 19:59.640
But we've taken heavy casualties too.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.240
The Marquis has ordered a full advance.

20:01.320 --> 20:03.360
-Understood. I'll go at once.
-Yes, sir.

20:03.440 --> 20:04.800
Brother Sun is the Strategist?

20:08.040 --> 20:09.280
I dare not hide it from you, Mrs. Fan.

20:09.360 --> 20:10.600
Sun Jin was just an alias.

20:10.680 --> 20:12.360
My full name is Gongsun Yin.

20:12.440 --> 20:14.200
I currently serve
as the Strategist for the Xie army.

20:14.280 --> 20:16.120
Military matters are urgent.
I'll explain later.

20:16.200 --> 20:17.240
Mr. Gongsun,

20:17.920 --> 20:20.000
I've cared for Yan Zheng's wounds before.

20:20.080 --> 20:21.760
I know how to prepare medicine and such.

20:22.280 --> 20:24.960
Why don't I stay
and help with the wounded?

20:27.400 --> 20:29.560
That works. Please,
make yourselves at home.

20:35.600 --> 20:36.440
Come here.

20:37.840 --> 20:40.800
Ning, do you know where Brother-in-law is?

20:57.240 --> 20:58.480
You were already badly wounded,

20:59.080 --> 21:00.560
and now you insist
on handling everything yourself.

21:00.640 --> 21:02.120
On top of that,
the enemy keeps harassing us.

21:02.200 --> 21:04.720
-I'm going to find some anesthetic.
-No need.

21:04.800 --> 21:07.360
Leave the medicine here for the soldiers.

21:08.000 --> 21:09.680
There are too many wounded in the camp.

21:10.280 --> 21:12.320
Move some of them to my main tent.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.160
But won't that interfere

21:14.240 --> 21:15.760
with your handling of military affairs?

21:15.840 --> 21:16.960
It won't.

21:18.360 --> 21:21.200
Move the lightly wounded to my main tent.
They won't be in the way.

21:21.280 --> 21:23.960
The freed-up tents
can be used for the seriously injured.

21:24.040 --> 21:24.880
But…

21:26.000 --> 21:27.280
Just do as I say.

21:28.280 --> 21:29.320
Yes, sir.

21:31.720 --> 21:33.640
Marquis, we've just finished
interrogating the enemy prisoners.

21:33.720 --> 21:36.360
According to them, the enemy plans
to attack the mountain at dawn.

21:39.000 --> 21:40.840
Here is easy to defend and hard to attack.

21:40.920 --> 21:42.160
Shi Yue isn't stupid.

21:43.200 --> 21:45.920
He'd never fight a battle where he loses
ten men for every one of ours.

21:46.720 --> 21:49.440
He just hasn't seen me for days

21:50.720 --> 21:52.000
and is using these troops

21:52.920 --> 21:54.680
to probe my condition.

22:04.080 --> 22:06.360
What happened next?
What happened to that bad man?

22:07.120 --> 22:09.200
I don't know.
After Brother-in-law saved me,

22:09.280 --> 22:11.800
Mr. Strategist took care of me.

22:11.880 --> 22:15.120
Sister, do you think
Bao'er and Pretty Lady will die?

22:15.800 --> 22:18.360
That big bad guy's brother is crazy.

22:18.440 --> 22:20.600
He's always bullying Pretty Lady.

22:20.680 --> 22:22.840
Bao'er has cried secretly many times.

22:23.520 --> 22:24.600
No, they won't.

22:24.680 --> 22:26.640
Aunt Qianqian and Bao'er are so clever.

22:26.720 --> 22:28.320
Once we find Brother-in-law,

22:28.400 --> 22:30.120
we'll go down the mountain together
and save them.

22:30.200 --> 22:31.240
-How about that?
-Okay.

22:34.600 --> 22:35.640
What are you doing here?

22:39.240 --> 22:41.800
I had nothing to do,
so I came to help prepare medicine.

22:41.880 --> 22:44.200
All the medicine in this shed
was personally tested

22:44.280 --> 22:46.920
and carefully prepared by us,
the imperial physicians.

22:48.040 --> 22:49.360
That's a lot.

22:49.440 --> 22:51.240
Are you really that sick?

22:52.480 --> 22:53.840
You don't get it.

22:53.920 --> 22:56.000
We physicians test the medicine ourselves

22:56.080 --> 22:58.480
to ensure it heals the soldiers properly.

22:58.560 --> 22:59.880
Supplies are scarce.

22:59.960 --> 23:01.280
This was all foraged from the mountain.

23:02.200 --> 23:05.280
By the way, you saved me last time.

23:06.680 --> 23:08.120
I want to say thank you.

23:08.200 --> 23:09.320
No need.

23:09.400 --> 23:10.880
I never asked your name.

23:11.480 --> 23:13.840
-My surname is Qi.
-Qi Bengong.

23:14.600 --> 23:15.920
Qi Bengong?

23:16.840 --> 23:18.000
That's an interesting name.

23:18.600 --> 23:19.440
You…

23:21.880 --> 23:23.920
Sister, who is she?

23:28.400 --> 23:30.560
She's Ms. Physician.

23:30.640 --> 23:33.880
You know, like the doctor who treats
the emperor in the shadow puppetry.

23:35.640 --> 23:37.400
Hello, Ms. Physician.

23:37.480 --> 23:38.560
Hello.

23:40.520 --> 23:43.040
But this is a battlefield.

23:43.120 --> 23:44.680
Why is your little sister here?

23:44.760 --> 23:47.320
My brother-in-law brought me here
to keep me safe.

23:49.280 --> 23:51.400
That is my husband. His name is Yan Zheng.

23:53.520 --> 23:55.360
No wonder you were so set
on coming up the mountain.

23:55.960 --> 23:56.880
So you came…

23:57.640 --> 23:58.920
chasing after your husband.

24:00.080 --> 24:01.880
I came up with the grain delivery.

24:01.960 --> 24:03.880
I just didn't expect Ning to be here.

24:04.600 --> 24:05.760
She said her brother-in-law was here too,

24:06.480 --> 24:07.960
but the camp is so big.

24:08.040 --> 24:09.520
I haven't been able to find him yet.

24:09.600 --> 24:11.760
My brother-in-law is so mighty!

24:11.840 --> 24:13.960
He saved me from the bad guys.

24:14.040 --> 24:16.640
He's even more impressive
than the generals in the shadow puppetry.

24:16.720 --> 24:17.640
Swish, swish,

24:17.720 --> 24:19.600
and all the bad guys were down.

24:20.200 --> 24:21.800
More impressive than the Marquis of Wu'an?

24:22.480 --> 24:23.840
My brother-in-law is the best.

24:24.520 --> 24:27.200
She's just a kid who's watched
too much shadow puppetry.

24:27.280 --> 24:29.720
How could he possibly be more impressive
than the Marquis of Wu'an?

24:29.800 --> 24:31.200
If he were that capable,

24:31.280 --> 24:33.680
he wouldn't be with
a pig-slaughtering woman like me.

24:40.080 --> 24:41.120
No need to tend to me.

24:42.000 --> 24:43.120
Go take care of them instead.

24:44.360 --> 24:46.000
And make sure they don't learn who I am.

24:46.760 --> 24:48.480
I don't want them to feel uncomfortable
while they recover.

24:48.560 --> 24:50.680
Understood. Get some rest for now.

25:08.320 --> 25:10.400
XIE

25:42.880 --> 25:43.760
Hey, little brother.

25:44.600 --> 25:45.880
What is this place?

25:45.960 --> 25:47.040
This is the camp for the lightly wounded.

25:47.640 --> 25:48.760
This is the camp for the lightly wounded.

25:52.320 --> 25:54.240
Hello. Is Li Gui here?

25:54.320 --> 25:55.160
The second one.

25:56.800 --> 25:59.000
Yours. Wang Fa.

25:59.800 --> 26:00.640
That's me.

26:02.080 --> 26:04.080
-Yours.
-Thanks.

26:04.600 --> 26:06.080
-Zhang Jian?
-I'm here.

26:06.760 --> 26:09.160
Yours. You need to take
two more doses of this medicine.

26:09.240 --> 26:10.960
One tonight and one tomorrow morning.

26:11.040 --> 26:12.720
These next two days, bundle up

26:12.800 --> 26:14.360
-and get plenty of rest.
-Okay.

26:17.400 --> 26:18.720
Drink up.

26:32.800 --> 26:34.280
Quick, go fetch my imperial physician.

26:34.360 --> 26:36.720
This man's wound has opened up.
It needs to be re-bandaged.

26:37.400 --> 26:38.240
Okay.

27:06.200 --> 27:07.240
Changyu.

27:11.480 --> 27:12.520
Yan Zheng.

27:20.600 --> 27:22.680
-I've been looking for you for so long.
-Stop.

27:30.160 --> 27:31.720
What are you doing here?

27:33.000 --> 27:34.280
I came looking for you.

27:35.440 --> 27:36.600
You came looking for me?

27:40.560 --> 27:42.080
Did it go down to the bone?

27:44.080 --> 27:45.280
What did the doctor say?

27:47.360 --> 27:48.520
It's just a light wound.

27:49.320 --> 27:50.600
Didn't reach the vital organs.

27:51.280 --> 27:52.840
A few days and I'll be fine.

28:00.200 --> 28:01.680
Getting hurt doesn't matter.

28:01.760 --> 28:03.320
Even if you're crippled, it's okay.

28:04.600 --> 28:07.200
Just leave the army and come home with me.

28:07.280 --> 28:09.200
I can slaughter pigs and support you.

28:15.280 --> 28:16.520
Hey, little brother,

28:16.600 --> 28:17.840
look at your luck.

28:18.440 --> 28:20.560
Having such a pretty wife
come all this way looking for you.

28:20.640 --> 28:21.680
If I were you,

28:21.760 --> 28:23.280
even if I kicked the bucket right now,

28:23.360 --> 28:24.480
it'd be worth it.

28:25.240 --> 28:26.240
Little lady,

28:26.320 --> 28:28.000
I know you care about your husband,

28:28.600 --> 28:30.120
but this is a military camp.

28:30.200 --> 28:32.360
Desertion means execution.

28:32.440 --> 28:34.560
We're under
the Marquis of Wu'an's command now.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.840
If we break the rules
and get our heads chopped off,

28:36.920 --> 28:39.120
-where will you find a handsome husband?
-Exactly.

28:41.240 --> 28:43.920
This little lady doesn't know
the rules, does she?

28:44.000 --> 28:45.440
Saying things like that.

28:45.520 --> 28:47.000
The Marquis is right in his tent.

28:47.080 --> 28:49.240
She might face military discipline.

28:50.280 --> 28:52.200
I wasn't trying to make you a deserter.

28:52.280 --> 28:55.600
I just spoke without thinking because
I was worried. Don't take it to heart.

28:56.280 --> 28:57.440
-I--
-I understand. I know.

28:57.520 --> 28:59.640
Quietly pass the order.
Assemble outside the tent.

29:00.480 --> 29:01.360
Don't cry.

29:03.840 --> 29:04.680
Strategist.

29:08.480 --> 29:10.520
Quietly pass the order.
Assemble outside the tent.

29:13.680 --> 29:15.480
Nice weather today.

29:18.480 --> 29:19.360
Let's go.

29:27.080 --> 29:29.800
Don't cry. It's okay. I understand.

29:35.320 --> 29:36.160
Strate--

29:40.920 --> 29:41.800
Does it hurt?

29:47.560 --> 29:48.600
With you here,

29:49.520 --> 29:50.840
it doesn't hurt.

30:02.920 --> 30:05.240
Why'd they all disappear just like that?

30:06.280 --> 30:07.680
Let's go.

30:07.760 --> 30:08.840
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

30:11.320 --> 30:13.800
I still need to report
the fodder situation to the Marquis.

30:13.880 --> 30:15.400
It can wait.

30:17.360 --> 30:20.920
The Marquis runs a tight camp. If I'm late
with the report, I'll get the lash.

30:22.000 --> 30:24.680
If you go in now, that's when
you'll really get the lash.

30:25.960 --> 30:28.600
Trust me. Wait an hour.

30:29.960 --> 30:32.720
I'm the brilliant strategist,
the genius of this army.

30:35.160 --> 30:36.760
Would I lie to you?

30:39.880 --> 30:40.800
Let's go.

30:42.720 --> 30:43.560
Changyu!

30:45.320 --> 30:46.720
You found your husband?

30:46.800 --> 30:49.000
I heard he was wounded.

30:49.080 --> 30:50.360
The Marquis of Wu'an is also injured.

30:50.440 --> 30:52.560
I should go see him first,

30:52.640 --> 30:55.040
but I came to you instead.
I was afraid you'd be worried.

30:55.120 --> 30:56.360
Thank you.

30:56.440 --> 30:57.280
Come.

31:00.280 --> 31:01.320
Yan Zheng,

31:01.880 --> 31:03.960
this is Miss Qi Bengong.

31:04.560 --> 31:06.880
She's beautiful and skilled in medicine.
She'll surely heal you.

31:11.480 --> 31:13.240
Is your husband him?

31:14.080 --> 31:15.880
The army medic you mentioned is her?

31:21.040 --> 31:23.800
What's wrong? My husband
is handsome, isn't he?

31:25.360 --> 31:27.120
Married?

31:28.800 --> 31:30.760
I never would have guessed.

31:31.680 --> 31:32.840
You two know each other?

31:33.960 --> 31:36.360
We've only just met.

31:37.200 --> 31:38.880
Then could you check on him now?

31:38.960 --> 31:39.920
No need.

31:41.360 --> 31:43.240
You don't trust me that much?

31:46.480 --> 31:48.360
Miss Bengong may be young,

31:49.160 --> 31:50.800
but she's extremely dedicated.

31:50.880 --> 31:53.200
She gives her all
to every wounded soldier.

31:59.720 --> 32:01.560
He actually married you?

32:02.200 --> 32:03.440
With a betrothal gift and everything?

32:04.240 --> 32:05.760
You're not being tricked, are you?

32:05.840 --> 32:08.000
Let me tell you.
There are so many frauds these days,

32:08.080 --> 32:09.920
especially the ones who trade
on their looks and live off women.

32:16.680 --> 32:18.280
He couldn't possibly deceive me.

32:18.960 --> 32:21.040
Do you see any internal injuries?

32:22.040 --> 32:23.640
I examined his wounds earlier.

32:23.720 --> 32:24.720
Nothing serious.

32:25.600 --> 32:27.440
But because the army
is short on medical supplies,

32:27.520 --> 32:29.480
lacking meat, lacking salt,

32:30.120 --> 32:31.560
his wounds are healing slowly.

32:32.200 --> 32:33.400
I've been testing
different medicines recently.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.000
I'll find suitable herbs
as soon as possible.

32:35.920 --> 32:36.920
Thank you, Bengong.

32:37.000 --> 32:39.400
Weren't you just saying you needed
to see the Marquis of Wu'an?

32:39.480 --> 32:40.560
You should go now.

32:42.840 --> 32:45.120
Then I won't intrude on your reunion.

32:46.280 --> 32:49.480
I'll go see the Marquis now.

32:53.040 --> 32:54.120
Come, Jianjia.

33:02.240 --> 33:04.560
What's wrong? You look pale.

33:05.400 --> 33:06.240
It's nothing.

33:06.960 --> 33:08.520
Why did you call her "Bengong"?

33:09.400 --> 33:12.160
That physician's surname is Qi.
Her given name is Bengong.

33:30.320 --> 33:31.840
This camp's short on everything.

33:31.920 --> 33:33.400
How is there not even one good fan?

33:37.720 --> 33:40.480
Your High… Physician, I've found a fan.

33:47.280 --> 33:48.200
Is this…

33:49.040 --> 33:50.280
Where did you find this fan?

33:50.880 --> 33:52.440
I took it from someone's hand.

33:52.520 --> 33:54.400
I was in a hurry and didn't see who.

33:56.520 --> 33:57.360
Your Highness.

34:02.360 --> 34:05.000
-Go find me another fan.
-Yes.

34:16.000 --> 34:17.400
I pay my respects to Your Highness.

34:18.560 --> 34:20.120
Headmaster Gongsun, long time no see.

34:21.440 --> 34:22.400
Long time no see.

34:25.800 --> 34:27.440
I just didn't expect to find

34:27.520 --> 34:29.560
Your Highness here in the military camp.

34:31.960 --> 34:34.120
-I…
-Surely not chasing after me?

34:34.840 --> 34:37.040
If Empress Dowager An
in the palace finds out,

34:37.120 --> 34:38.360
she'll be worried sick.

34:42.120 --> 34:44.440
Headmaster, such speculation
is rather presumptuous, don't you think?

34:45.360 --> 34:46.679
You and the Marquis

34:46.760 --> 34:49.040
came here to quell the rebellion
and make your name.

34:49.760 --> 34:50.840
Am I…

34:52.400 --> 34:53.480
as the physician,

34:54.080 --> 34:56.800
only fit to be confined
within the palace walls,

34:57.400 --> 34:59.000
fussing over trivial, meaningless matters?

34:59.880 --> 35:00.880
I overstepped.

35:00.960 --> 35:03.240
Physician, I've brought the fan.

35:14.560 --> 35:15.680
Headmaster, is there something else?

35:17.200 --> 35:18.440
No. I…

35:23.000 --> 35:23.880
I'll take my leave now.

35:36.520 --> 35:37.360
Get back to work.

35:52.680 --> 35:54.880
This is the camp for the lightly wounded.
Miss, you're…?

35:54.960 --> 35:56.120
My husband is inside.

35:56.200 --> 35:57.960
-I need to change his bandages.
-Leave us.

36:06.200 --> 36:07.360
You two officers…

36:11.440 --> 36:12.880
Haven't we met before?

36:15.200 --> 36:17.360
I've traveled far and wide
and met plenty of people,

36:17.440 --> 36:18.600
but I've never seen you before.

36:19.560 --> 36:21.560
Lady, you must have
mistaken me for someone else.

36:23.400 --> 36:25.520
That's right. You definitely
have the wrong person.

36:26.120 --> 36:28.720
They're my comrades,

36:29.320 --> 36:30.560
Wu and Qi.

36:31.640 --> 36:32.480
So you're his brothers.

36:33.160 --> 36:34.440
Thank you for looking after Yan Zheng.

36:35.360 --> 36:36.640
Don't mention it.

36:36.720 --> 36:37.760
Yan Zheng,

36:37.840 --> 36:39.480
you take good care of yourself
and rest up.

36:39.560 --> 36:41.360
We'll head out now. Take care.

37:01.680 --> 37:02.520
Bear with it.

37:42.680 --> 37:43.600
Does it hurt?

37:45.800 --> 37:46.880
It's okay.

37:51.360 --> 37:54.160
I really should have signed
that divorce letter with you sooner.

38:02.080 --> 38:03.400
Why are you spitting up blood?

38:07.120 --> 38:08.880
You really want to divorce me that badly?

38:14.640 --> 38:16.640
No divorce.

38:17.960 --> 38:19.440
I thought

38:20.040 --> 38:21.600
if you hadn't married into my family,

38:22.640 --> 38:24.240
you wouldn't have been conscripted.

38:24.920 --> 38:26.960
If we'd signed that divorce letter sooner,

38:28.480 --> 38:30.480
you wouldn't have been
taken by the soldiers

38:30.560 --> 38:32.200
and you wouldn't be hurt.

38:34.880 --> 38:36.360
Mr. Zhao told me…

38:38.440 --> 38:40.120
not to leave things unsettled

38:40.200 --> 38:41.760
as I grow old.

38:42.800 --> 38:44.880
When I came, I'd already made up my mind.

38:46.320 --> 38:47.680
If you're alive,

38:49.240 --> 38:50.960
we go home together.

38:51.040 --> 38:52.600
If you died…

38:54.760 --> 38:56.080
I'd bury you.

38:57.400 --> 38:58.880
And on every holiday,

38:59.920 --> 39:01.680
I'd burn joss paper for you.

39:07.160 --> 39:08.240
I knew it.

39:21.040 --> 39:22.360
That night…

39:23.400 --> 39:24.800
I shouldn't have treated you that way.

39:35.600 --> 39:37.280
You know it now?

39:40.960 --> 39:42.560
I got over it a long time ago.

39:47.280 --> 39:48.200
Xie Zheng.

39:49.960 --> 39:50.960
Zheng…

39:52.440 --> 39:55.200
Long time no see, brother Yan Zheng.

39:57.760 --> 40:00.120
Didn't expect to find
Mrs. Fan here as well.

40:00.200 --> 40:02.120
Apologies for interrupting.
I'll take my leave.

40:02.760 --> 40:03.720
No need to leave.

40:05.720 --> 40:07.400
The water's cold. I'll go change it.

40:11.200 --> 40:13.960
As for meat… I'll figure something out.

40:26.280 --> 40:28.720
This injury of yours really paid off.

40:29.680 --> 40:32.240
I saw it all. Mrs. Fan
was crying her eyes out.

40:32.320 --> 40:33.440
And you just…

40:33.520 --> 40:34.600
Move aside.

40:45.200 --> 40:46.600
-I'm here to talk business.
-Talk.

40:49.040 --> 40:50.800
That Sui Yuanqing,

40:50.880 --> 40:53.880
he thought to use Mrs. Fan's
little sister to threaten you.

40:54.560 --> 40:56.640
If word of Mrs. Fan

40:56.720 --> 40:58.400
reaches Chancellor Wei's ears,

40:59.840 --> 41:01.600
with his ways…

41:01.680 --> 41:03.200
You know his methods.

41:05.120 --> 41:07.640
Keep today's events contained.

41:08.440 --> 41:09.760
Nothing gets out.

41:12.000 --> 41:14.520
The Xie family guards are tight-lipped.

41:14.600 --> 41:17.200
The soldiers on the front
don't know what you look like.

41:18.760 --> 41:20.080
But they do know

41:20.160 --> 41:24.200
Mrs. Fan came to camp
and found her husband.

41:27.600 --> 41:28.800
Better…

41:29.640 --> 41:31.200
assign me a separate tent.

41:32.160 --> 41:33.400
Just in case.

41:36.400 --> 41:38.760
Is that to keep your identity from leaking

41:39.360 --> 41:40.800
or to steal some sweet moments?

41:43.480 --> 41:44.440
Let's be serious.

41:45.040 --> 41:47.160
How long do you plan
to keep this from her?

41:51.520 --> 41:53.600
I'll find the right time to tell her.

41:55.640 --> 41:57.240
A young lady

41:58.040 --> 42:00.760
braves danger to come to the battlefield
looking for her husband.

42:00.840 --> 42:03.440
Such loyalty and devotion
doesn't deserve to be kept in the dark.

44:46.920 --> 44:50.080
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

44:50.160 --> 44:51.080
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
